      "title": "Stock market down",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Colombo stock market showed a downward trend yesterday (17th), and at the end of the day, the all share price index was recorded as 8,907.89, down by 178.89 points.",
        "S. The &P index also fell by 90.59 points, with a daily turnover of 3.7 billion rupees."
